sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant API as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VWH as Validating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODH as odh-notebook-controller
    participant KF as notebook-controller
    participant GW as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NB as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant ImgReg as OpenShift Image Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,ImgReg: Flow 1: Notebook Creation (RHOAI 3.x)
        User->>API: POST Notebook CR<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
        API->>MWH: Admission (mutate)<br/>8443/TCP, TLS (service-ca), mTLS
        MWH->>API: ImageStream lookup<br/>443/TCP, SA token
        API->>ImgReg: Resolve image tag<br/>5000/TCP, HTTPS
        ImgReg-->>API: Docker image reference
        API-->>MWH: ImageStream response
        Note over MWH: Injects: kube-rbac-proxy sidecar,<br/>CA cert bundles, proxy env vars,<br/>pipeline config, MLflow env, Feast config
        MWH-->>API: Mutated Notebook
        API->>VWH: Admission (validate)<br/>8443/TCP, TLS (service-ca), mTLS
        Note over VWH: Validates MLflow annotation<br/>not removed on running notebook
        VWH-->>API: Allowed
        API-->>User: Notebook created
        API->>ODH: Watch event (Notebook)
        ODH->>API: Create HTTPRoute, ReferenceGrant,<br/>NetworkPolicy, ServiceAccount,<br/>Service, ConfigMap, ClusterRoleBinding<br/>443/TCP, SA token
        API->>KF: Watch event (Notebook)
        KF->>API: Create StatefulSet, Service<br/>443/TCP, SA token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,NB: Flow 2: Notebook Access (RHOAI 3.x with kube-rbac-proxy)
        User->>GW: GET /notebook/...<br/>443/TCP, HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
        GW->>KRBAC: HTTPRoute → kube-rbac-proxy Service<br/>8443/TCP, HTTPS (service-ca cert)
        KRBAC->>API: TokenReview<br/>443/TCP, HTTPS, SA token
        API-->>KRBAC: Token valid
        KRBAC->>API: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get notebooks.kubeflow.org)
        API-->>KRBAC: Authorized
        KRBAC->>NB: Proxy request<br/>8888/TCP, HTTP (localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header
        NB-->>KRBAC: Response
        KRBAC-->>GW: Response
        GW-->>User: Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over KF,NB: Flow 3: Idle Notebook Culling
        loop Every IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD (default: 1 min)
            KF->>NB: GET /api/kernels<br/>80/TCP, HTTP, No auth
            NB-->>KF: Kernel list (JSON)
            KF->>NB: GET /api/terminals<br/>80/TCP, HTTP, No auth
            NB-->>KF: Terminal list (JSON)
            Note over KF: Check last activity time<br/>vs CULL_IDLE_TIME (default: 1440 min)
        end
        Note over KF: Notebook idle → set stop annotation
        KF->>API: PATCH Notebook (stop annotation)<br/>443/TCP, HTTPS, SA token
        KF->>API: Scale StatefulSet to 0<br/>443/TCP, HTTPS, SA token
    end
